Quickstrike:



Quickstrike blinked awake, and stretched his arms and legs out as he 
did so. His optic sensors adjusted to the darkness of the bunker, and 
saw Black Arachnia lying by him. He grinned and slid closer to her. 
He rested his head on her shoulder, thinking things were going to be 
fine. If she was in a good mood enough to do what she did a few hours 
ago, things were going to turn out just fine. 

He watched as she slept and leaned up, kissing her forehead. He laid 
his head back on her shoulder. He wanted to stay by her until she 
woke. He looked down her body then put his cobra arm over her chest.

While lying still, he got hungry. He glowered a little. He would have 
to wait.
